        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/18073813-the-invisible-man">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7125124-jess-harbinger-of-blood-soaked-rainbows?shelf=the-list">the-list</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7125124-jess-harbinger-of-blood-soaked-rainbows?shelf=2-and-a-half-stars">2-and-a-half-stars</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7125124-jess-harbinger-of-blood-soaked-rainbows?shelf=for-kindle">for-kindle</a>, 
